{"tid":492654,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[修正重發] 何氏老妖喪母 即刻整隻<舊歡如夢>賀賀佢","createTime":"2017-12-07T18:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T18:03:28.000Z","uid":102814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1caf716c6c613d9ec2ae4de40089bdd8c238fe41","tid":492654,"uid":102814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T18:03:28.000Z","msg":"&lt;愛君 &middot; 堯夢&gt;<br />\n<br />\n_  _  今晚母仙遊　直奔遠洋路<br />\n禱告世間願安息　觀音此際沒法力<br />\n難敵傷心哭青煙　露甘愛蓮葉<br />\n因故強忍未哀問　手執此塊是哪葉<br />\n <br />\n酒巡千杯懶銷愁　禍福最是難料<br />\n高喊殺機滅港獨　天官不赦落降頭<br />\n寧聚口德敬先妣　爛口惹仇恨<br />\n妖獸化妝辨畜牲　畜牲早已在眼前<br />\n<br />\n親情於今化煙雲　未許再續情份<br />\n倒米孝子為安樂　上香不會是拜神<br />\n其實因果真不公　是非無人認<br />\n鄉議局再三起風波　告君恩怨問阿堯<br />\n看倌今世勿姓何　偲嫣終究亦嫁人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IeBWKRynfn0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIeBWKRynfn0&d=W%2Bs0AQgvD%2Bcf6t2x4TcuGv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=55ce38a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IeBWKRynfn0</a>"}]}